\section{Module theia.rendering.features}

    \label{theia:rendering:features}
Features module or theia, to represent objects as FreeCAD Python features.

%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
